cted","react-hooks/exhaustive-deps","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'dispatch'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.","ArrayExpression",["148"],["146"],["147"],"'dispatch' is assigned a value but never used.","'basket' is assigned a value but never used.","'payload' is assigned a value but never used.","no-global-assign","no-unsafe-negation",{"desc":"149","fix":"150"},"Update the dependencies array to be: [dispatch]",{"range":"151","text":"152"},[1208,1210],"[dispatch]"]